nity driven events to keep events free and open to new contributing members. Companies can find <a href="https://en.opensuse.org/images/9/94/OSC25prospectus.pdf">;sponsorship information</a>; or <a href="https://geekos.org/sponsorship/">;donate to the Geeko Foundation</a>; to assist with funds that will go toward the conference.</p>; <meta name="openSUSE, board, community, conference, event, sponsors" content="HTML,CSS,XML,JavaScript" />;
